Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:20.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The universe stretches out infinitely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fumizuki Academy is a{\i0}\N{\i1}prep school created to ensure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that its students could survive{\i0}\N{\i1}fiercely competitive entrance exams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:28.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, it is a training{\i0}\N{\i1}school for academic warriors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who fight using academic{\i0}\N{\i1}performance as their weapon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Putting their class' prestige on the line,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they fight by making maximal{\i0}\N{\i1}use of the subjects they are good at{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:39.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and overrun their enemy's strategic facilities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:41.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those with power win accolades,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:45.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and receive praise and the right{\i0}\N{\i1}to enjoy an elegant school life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those without ability fall mercilessly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:50.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and are forced to live an unspeakable hell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:58.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the story of academic warriors{\i0}\N{\i1}who stand up to such a cruel fate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:04.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And here is what happened to{\i0}\N{\i1}the losers of a Summoner Test War.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:08.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Even after my student discount,\Na movie ticket costs 1000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,A medium Coke is 300 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,A small popcorn is 400 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,And all that only lasts 2 hours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,How frightening these movie theaters are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:22.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh... What is it, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you like... to see this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.46,0:01:27.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh I see, that looks good.\NLet's see this one, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:32.26,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Really? Then don't worry\Nabout me. You two go see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:34.59,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?! Why?!\N--What?! Why is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:35.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Then do you want to see an anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:37.68,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:40.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Just give it up, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:44.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Men are... powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:45.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:47.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, which one would you like to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:49.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna be free soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:51.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, {\i1}Apocalypse Now Redux{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:54.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! That lasts 3 hours and 23 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:55.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll watch it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,That's longer than all\Nthe day's classes combined!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:02:03.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Since I can't see you during\Nclasses, I'm making up for lost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:04.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Definitely going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:06.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Today... I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What, Shouko?!\NWhat's that?! What?! Ah! Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Two student tickets for\Nthe next two showings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:16.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! So one student\Nand one unconscious student
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:17.43,Main,,0,0,0,,to watch it twice for no good reason, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What a happy couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you just adore couples like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:32.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What grows on its own? Hmm, what is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one more{\i0}\N{\i1}chance. Never never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:38.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one{\i0}\N{\i1}more chance. Never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:47.38,Main,,0,0,0,,BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:51.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Nice to encounter you,"{\i0}\N{\i1}that one's too easy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's only one answer{\i0}\N{\i1}that I decided on at the start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart fluttered. Will I pass?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:59.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't panic whether{\i0}\N{\i1}it's a matter of love or war{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:01.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sigh as I cram all night long{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:04.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a genius dreamer inside of me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:07.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'd be nice if everything I wanted came true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pay no mind to other people's worlds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area complete!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll definitely be waiting right here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:21.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area, I can hear someone wishing for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah! Ear! Ear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:25.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? We just keep missing each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:28.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you came to me for advice, it'd go like{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"So, friends?" "Yes, friends."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a sad 0 points.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:36.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Do it again! Rewrite it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I'm serious, one{\i0}\N{\i1}more chance please{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:43.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, there's a future{\i0}\N{\i1}more wonderful than now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:49.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it more wonderful than{\i0}\N{\i1}now... my life, my life, my life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akihisa Yoshii. His parents{\i0}\N{\i1}are working overseas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His older sister is studying abroad{\i0}\N{\i1}and does not live at home, either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he was fully enjoying{\i0}\N{\i1}a carefree life living alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:06.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess for breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I should eat light so I can have\Na bigger meal for dinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:15.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I'll eat this one for breakfast\Nand eat the slightly bigger one for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was fully enjoying it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:28.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Good morning, Mr. Fukuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:30.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:57.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You're Yoshii from Class F!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.76,Main,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\Nyou're Kubo from Class A?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:06.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right! I'm Year 2's\NNo. 2 student, Toshimitsu Kubo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:09.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no. I'd better hurry up or I won't\Nhave time to prepare for the first class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.02,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hey!\N--What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That... you don't need that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:17.40,Main,,0,0,0,,No... I guess not, since\Nit can't be eaten any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What? You don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To think that he wants{\i0}\N{\i1}something I took a bite out of...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-If I pick it up within{\i0}\N{\i1}30 seconds, it'll be fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I do mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:39.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You're too bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Others are... watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Then... see you some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:52.27,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:03.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did I step on something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes... my lifeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning, Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:19.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! G-Good morning, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:26.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that... a love letter\Nto give to Yuuji after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:29.39,Main,,0,0,0,,But Yuuji's got Kirishima, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:32.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're early for a change, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:32.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.19,Main,,0,0,0,,How was yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.14,Main,,0,0,0,,This month's food budget disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:38.06,Main,,0,0,0,,into the darkness of the\Nmovie theater in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:43.07,Main,,0,0,0,,When I woke up, it was a scene\Nwhere a buffalo tied to a pole was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:43.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:45.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I tried to find a chance to run,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,but I got an electric shock\Nagain and became unconscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.49,Main,,0,0,0,,And when I woke up, the buffalo was again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,So you guys really watched it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.83,Main,,0,0,0,,If I try to run again, I might\Nlose consciousness again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I was seized by this compulsive\Nidea and thought I might forever wake to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:01.55,Main,,0,0,0,,the scene where they kill the buffalo,\Nso I became unable to run any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,So you'll never be able to see\Nthe first part of the movie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,how am I gonna survive until I get\Nmoney from my parents next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You can sell that mountain\Nof video games you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Those are irreplaceable, excellent works!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.81,Main,,0,0,0,,How could I ever exchange\Nthem for something like food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:20.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know the saying,\N"You reap what you sow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You can say that because\Nyou still have breathing room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,In my case, it's a life-or-death situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you really think that my life isn't at risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:37.83,Main,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:45.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I never thought... that our equipment\Nwould get worse than that. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Complaining about the outcome\Nof everyone working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What an unrefined guy you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You lost all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you saying, Aki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not in a position to talk, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:01.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Neither of us were any help\Nat all in the war, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:02.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Lady Minami, too, had poor judgment\Nso Hideyoshi's older sister was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.40,Main,,0,0,0,,--My skull feels like it's about\Nto split! Ow, ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.24,Main,,0,0,0,,--What's with this "Lady" Minami?! Are you mocking me?\N--My skull feels like it's about to split! Ow, ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.07,Main,,0,0,0,,--What's with this "Lady" Minami?! Are you mocking me?\N--But you told me to call you that! Hey! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.57,Main,,0,0,0,,--Call me just Minami!\N--But you told me to call you that! Hey! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:16.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Minami had poor judgment so... Ow, ow,\Now...! You're gonna shatter my temples!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.37,Main,,0,0,0,,This technique... is no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.59,Main,,0,0,0,,But he was the key to our strategy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:26.80,Main,,0,0,0,,and yet he couldn't get 100%\Nin an elementary school level test!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:30.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't blame Sakamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the problem? I like... this classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:38.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it... Himeji really likes Yuuji...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:43.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...because in this classroom,{\i0}\N{\i1}I can sit anywhere I want.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:45.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ding-dang-dong...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:48.24,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, then! Time for homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:51.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone, have a seat!\NOh, you're all sitting, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Why are you here, Mr. Nishimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you guys are so stupid, we\Nwanted to bring up your scores a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:02.42,Main,,0,0,0,,So, it was decided that I,\Nthe one in charge of remedial classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:04.88,Main,,0,0,0,,will replace Mr. Fukuhara as Class F\Nhomeroom teacher starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,And it was also decided\Nthat I'll be the narrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Iron Man is our homeroom teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll mercilessly and vigorously put you\Nthrough the wringer. So be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Now it's like every day is\Na remedial class by a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wonder if there's\Nsomething that can be done about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:29.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! All we have to do is fight\Nin a Summoner Test War again and win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:31.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Once a class loses, the rules forbid\Nthem to declare a war for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Three...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, three months will pass in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll come up with a new\Nstrategy in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.88,Main,,0,0,0,,There are good things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,500 yen per pic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,--Thanks, as always!\N--Whoa! This is an original pic! The Round Card Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.26,Main,,0,0,0,,--What about your food budget?\N--Whoa! This is an original pic! The Round Card Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:58.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:09:59.64,Main,,0,0,0,,"Secret Photo Album, Vol. 3"\N"2-F Akihisa Yoshii"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a man! I have no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:02.94,Main,,0,0,0,,What a brave man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Now it's certain that I'll have one cup\Nnoodle per day until I get more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa... Aren't you forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:14.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aki. When and where\Nshould we meet up this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:19.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Meet... up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you forgot about it.\NYou promised to treat me to crepes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:27.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! D-Didn't treating you yesterday cover it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:30.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yesterday is yesterday. Promise is promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.72,Main,,0,0,0,,May I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! You too, Himeji?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:38.14,Main,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, there's a\Nmovie I want to see with you, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:41.73,Main,,0,0,0,,M... My... food budget...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:48.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiot Test!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, the weekend after{\i0}\N{\i1}the new narrator started...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:57.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cup noodle artisans start working early.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That one's for dinner and this one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:04.75,Main,,0,0,0,,First, I cut it in half and eat one half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Then next time, I cut the\Nremaining half in half and eat one half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,And then, the next time, too, I cut that\Nin half and eat one half. If I keep doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I can eat one cup noodle forever! I might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.18,Main,,0,0,0,,a genius...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was fully enjoying it in a lot of ways.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Even so, I can't waste money, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! When you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,isn't going out for movies or\Nhaving crepes with girls... a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:42.33,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is a date!\NIt's not a punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, spending a little money
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.96,Main,,0,0,0,,shouldn't be a problem at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:12:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it... It's a punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I was being beaten\Ndown by the absurdity of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mizuki! That outfit is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:18.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But I spent so much time picking\Nan outfit that I was almost late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:21.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't make up my mind what\Nto wear, either, until just earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I can still\Nwear the shirt from last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. In other words,\Nsince last year, you haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,My knees are about to be twisted in a wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I didn't say anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:36.72,Main,,0,0,0,,--I know what you were going to say, so what's the problem?!\N--Ow, ow, ow...! Rope! Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Almost...! Almost...! Almost...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What's Muttsulini doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Independent training.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What would you like to see, Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You can pick today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.14,Main,,0,0,0,,They all cost the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:52.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Then maybe a longer one is a better deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you wanna see, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:59.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Will my wish... be granted?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, {\i1}War and Peace{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, that lasts 7 hours and 4 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:03.87,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll watch it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can keep\Nsitting for 14 hours and 8 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:09.37,Main,,0,0,0,,If you get bored... you\Ncan take a nap next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,--You mean lose consciousness, right?!\N--Don't worry. I'll be with you the whole time so it's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Two student tickets for the next two showings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! So one student and\None unconscious student again
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.55,Main,,0,0,0,,to watch it twice for no good reason, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:22.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I envy those who can openly\Nexpress their feeling to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:24.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you just adore couples like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll pick a shorter one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're not eating, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.39,Main,,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, actually, I'm particular\Nabout food and crepes are not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.57,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Someone who'd try to eat bread\Noff the ground would say that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:41.57,MainTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to save even a little here or{\i0}\N{\i1}I'll have no money to buy food tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.32,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"You should just be honest and\Ntell them you don't have money."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:47.28,MainTop,,0,0,0,,I see... My banana crepe\Nis a little too much for me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.75,MainTop,,0,0,0,,so I wanted you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:56.46,MainTop,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to have a bite of\Nmy strawberry crepe, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.63,MainTop,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:59.17,MainTop,,0,0,0,,If you don't like crepes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:02.59,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.68,MainTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stupid me! Why did I have to do that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:06.68,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"See, I told you..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.22,MainTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My chance for a mouth-to-mouth{\i0}\N{\i1}crepe from Himeji was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.39,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Well, this isn't that kind of game, is it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:12.89,MainTop,,0,0,0,,At the least, with just that one bite,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.31,MainTop,,0,0,0,,I could've gotten more\Ncalories than my breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:18.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try just a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.11,Main,,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:23.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I-If you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:26.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yoshii! Have mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Mine's first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:31.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's a matter of who goes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:38.29,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,To think that you give your sweet, sweet crepe
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,to that filthy domestic animal with\Nthe fork that you put in your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't let it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:51.06,Main,,0,0,0,,In order for this pig to no longer\Nget carried away and behave rudely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Er... a pig?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:54.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll bring him to justice right here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,"Theory of English Grammar"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Out of my way! Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:03.36,Main,,0,0,0,,"Bam!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:09.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! The crepes are...!\NIt hasn't been 30 seconds yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold it, you pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:12.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Miharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Please wait for me, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yoshii... You made my face dirty...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:23.59,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Sarukashira Park"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What did I do to deserve this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,She's special, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:28.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Special?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:31.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Akihisa! What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:36.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You pig! Where'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Get your scent on my honey
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:41.02,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'll burn you to death immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:44.24,Main,,0,0,0,,--Where'd you go?! That way?! This way?!\N--Wh-Why are you avoiding me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, she said she'd burn me to death, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.45,Main,,0,0,0,,--but are you guys running away from someone?\N--That way?! This way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:54.12,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yeah. Is there a good way to run away from her?\N--Or... this way?! This way?! This way?! Which way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish I could at least use my Avatar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:16:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,--We can't use the summoning system outside of academy premises.\N--You pig! You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. I happen to have an\Noutfit from my drama club with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.88,Main,,0,0,0,,--Why don't you put this on as a disguise?\N--You pig! You pig! You pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:12.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not a guy's outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:15.39,Main,,0,0,0,,The club members said it was for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.27,Main,,0,0,0,,so I just assumed that it was a guy's outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.81,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way an outfit for\Nyou would be guy's clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.19,Main,,0,0,0,,He somehow looks really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.73,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this sense of defeat I'm feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:27.57,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:30.57,Main,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop resisting and...\NWhat's with that appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't ask! It's hard to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That's filthy! How impure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,If you think that dressing like a girl is\Nall it takes to get my honey to like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,you're dead wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's you who's dead wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Like normal girls, I like guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:48.26,Main,,0,0,0,,How dare you profane my sacred\Nrelationship with my honey, you pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:52.64,Main,,0,0,0,,What'd I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like it backfired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:57.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, there is a bright side...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:59.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What do we do? She's still chasing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:02.23,Main,,0,0,0,,We're out of options.\NLet's split into three and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:04.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean that\NI'll become her only target?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:08.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! I've got an idea!\NLet's escape to Fumizuki Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:09.78,Main,,0,0,0,,To the Academy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I found a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:16.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Ms. Takeuchi teaches modern Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:18.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't be any help at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.96,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to be picky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ms. Takeuchi! We'd like\Nto fight a mock ST War.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, okay. I approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm summoning my Avatar... Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm summoning my Avatar. Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm summoning my Avatar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! How mean! Are you\Ntrying to hinder my love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:01.46,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as we have Himeji's\NAvatar, there's nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.75,Main,,0,0,0,,We can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimizu, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Not so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.67,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:13.26,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:17.31,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mizuki, Minami, Akihisa Win"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who died with their score reduced\Nto zero will be given a remedial class!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Today's a holiday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:27.48,Main,,0,0,0,,To me, even a remedial class by\Na demon is heaven if I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,--I'm with my honey!\N--I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:31.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii! Have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,discovered your true self?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wonder if Minami and Shimizu are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimizu might be happy being with Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii... About today... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:59.01,Main,,0,0,0,,We dragged you around...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But I had a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:06.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... I had fun, too, Himeji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:11.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You really are a kind person, you've\Nbeen that way since elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.74,Main,,0,0,0,,The time we took the placement test, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,When I left in the middle of the test,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:19.70,Main,,0,0,0,,you talked to the teacher,\Nsaying that giving me zero points
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,just because I had to leave the\Nroom due to sickness wasn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,But he said staying healthy to get\Nready for the test is also part of the test...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.67,Main,,0,0,0,,So it didn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.55,Main,,0,0,0,,About the Summoner\NTest War the other day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:35.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You suggested that for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:36.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakamoto told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:42.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:44.85,Main,,0,0,0,,very happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:56.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... about the letter you\Nwere writing the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You're talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:06.62,Main,,0,0,0,,This letter is... an unhappy chain letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:15.55,Main,,0,0,0,,that if you don't mail it out within\Nthree days, you'll become unhappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:21.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't have the courage to mail it...\Nso three days have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Feeling this much pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:30.31,Main,,0,0,0,,This might really be an\Nunhappy chain letter like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:34.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hime... ji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,If you like... I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.45,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Someday for sure... I'll deliver\Nthis to him myself, with my own will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Someday... for sure...\NWill you give me your support?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:59.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll be praying\Nthat it'll work out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-A-K-A Go Go Home!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:15.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-A-K-A Go Go Home!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The end of the school day is bliss{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:21.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I am to put it into words, "It's really angelic!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:24.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My peace was shattered{\i0}\N{\i1}by a sudden announcement{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talking about the make up test. "This is Hell!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:30.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While my friends and I were{\i0}\N{\i1}sharing funny stories, I said,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"There's no way anyone is that stupid"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:37.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the truth is, deep down in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:41.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was shouting, "That was me!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:47.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About that "Monthly Parking"{\i0}\N{\i1}sign you see in the parking lot{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:53.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought it was the name of a company...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:56.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All this time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:59.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sticking to your idiocy can be cool{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:02.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is our common sense nonsense?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:05.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't need rules in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:08.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's dog eat dog food! It's social upheaval!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:10.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:14.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sun that rose from the west is setting{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:17.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Run home! It's dinner time already.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go home! Let's go home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:37.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:39.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At any rate, he was fully enjoying it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:41.90,Main,,0,0,0,,"Yoshii"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? I wonder what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see... "To Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:51.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You might be surprised\Nto receive a letter like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm writing this because\NI wanted to tell you my true feelings."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:23:00.63,Main,,0,0,0,,This... is... a... love letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.92,0:23:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"You're always cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:07.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I've come to realize that seeing your\Ncheerful face makes me feel at ease."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:09.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.56,0:23:14.85,Main,,0,0,0,,"One day, I'd like to express my manly\Nfeelings to you. Please accept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:18.27,Main,,0,0,0,,To my dear Yoshii..." I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! "Manly"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.57,0:23:22.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It's from a guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:27.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Akihisa, who did you get the letter from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.16,0:23:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gone! The letter is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:31.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I had an original photo\Nthat I just bought in it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:37.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh... well... The sender's\N(my) name isn't on it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:41.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Noooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:46.22,Main,,0,0,0,,On top of that, even an\Noriginal photo was enclosed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:49.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:53.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Question 4.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:56.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is described as{\i0}\N{\i1}"made of spice and all things nice"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:23:59.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in one of the Mother Goose songs?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:00.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Curry and rice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.15,0:24:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Little girls are not food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:04.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode! "Love, Spices, and Boxed Lunches!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:05.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will be on the test.{\i0}
